    example: `If you have a $300,000 mortgage at an initial rate of 4% that adjusts after five years, this calculator shows how your payment changes if the rate jumps to 6% thereafter. You can see exactly how much your monthly obligation increases, allowing you to plan your household budget accordingly.`,
